title: Jack Teanby
text:
Jack Teanby (born 14 May 1996) is a professional <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer who plays as a <a href="Rugby%20league%20positions%23Prop">prop</a> for the <a href="York%20City%20Knights">York City Knights</a> in the <a href="Betfred%20Championship">Betfred Championship</a>. Sponsored by the bootham tavern social club
He previously played for the <a href="Dewsbury%20Rams">Dewsbury Rams</a> in the Championship.
Background.
Teanby was born in <a href="Leeds">Leeds</a>, <a href="West%20Yorkshire%2C%20England">West Yorkshire, England</a>.
Career.
In October 2018 he signed a one-year deal to join the York City Knights.
